However what I got was a guy who is nothing but filler in a group.  I can't take any hits and I can't deal much damage to speak of.<br>
What I think BMs need is a bonus to CD that allows us to actually use our offhand weapon up to 80% of the time.  I would much rather hit really fast and alot for small dmg then be put on a Hero's dmg table.<br>
I do agree we should be able to outdamage the Hero's but not be anywhere near as good at defense.<br>
Mostly I just want to be wanted. =/ <p>~ Accualt<br>
