s is ridiculous (and yes, I'm going up against critters weak against slash and I'm spec'd quite well). When my hero was 38, he could take just about every critter my 41 BM could easier and faster (sans buffs and end song for both). Kinda sad IMO. They definitely need to crank up our damage and put the detaunt style as front facing. Even if I'm not the main tank, I can still be in front of the thing detaunting to insure I don't get aggro. If I do get aggro, how exactly do I get behind it to detaunt since every mob auto-faces?? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Elrias Hugfiend</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#000000>(1/17/03 7:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=69.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> will mythic fix the bm?</span><hr size=1> The question we are all pondering is will Mythic do something about our complaints? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=skorj>Skorj</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 48<br> <font color=#000000>(1/20/03 9:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=69.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: will mythic fix the bm?</span><hr size=1> I heard rumors from rangers that CD was being looked at - anyone hear anyhting more substantial?  CD's been &quot;looked at&quot; for 14 months now, lol.<br>
